file.content:
openapi: "3.0.0"
info:
  version: 1.0.0
  title: mockApiTest
  license:
    name: MIT
servers:
  - url: /
x-wso2-basePath: /mockApiTest/1.0.0
paths:
  /testMockApi:
    get:
      summary: Tests Choreo Connect mock API implementation
      operationId: testImpl
      responses:
        '50X':
          description: Expected response to a valid request
          content:
            text/html:
              examples:
                example1:
                  value:
                    description: content for example 1
                example2:
                  value:
                    description: content for example 2
            application/xml:
              example:
                description: choreo connect
          headers:
            x-wso2-header:
              schema:
                type: string
              example: Sample header value
        'default':
          description: Expected response to a valid request
          content:
            application/json:
              example:
                description: default content
          headers:
            x-wso2-header:
              schema:
                type: string
              example: Sample header value
      security:
        - APIKeyAuth: [ ]
  /testOneExample:
    get:
      x-wso2-disable-security: true
      summary: Tests Choreo Connect mock API implementation with query parameters
      operationId: testImpl2
      responses:
        '500':
          description: only one example code for the resource
          content:
            application/json:
              examples:
                example1:
                  value:
                    description: json mediatype example1
          headers:
            x-wso2-header:
              schema:
                type: string
              example: Sample header value
      security:
        - APIKeyAuth: [ ]
  /testMockDefault:
    get:
      summary: Tests Choreo Connect mock default API implementation
      operationId: testImpl3
      responses:
        '200':
          description: Internal error
          content:
            application/json:
              schema:
                $ref: "#/components/schemas/Data"
              example:
                name: choreo connect
          headers:
            x-wso2-default-header:
              schema:
                type: string
              example: Default header value
      security:
        - APIKeyAuth: []
components:
  securitySchemes:
    APIKeyAuth:
      type: apiKey
      name: x-api-key
      in: header
  schemas:
    Data:
      type: object
      required:
        - id
        - name
      properties:
        id:
          type: integer
          format: int64
        name:
          type: string
        tag:
          type: string
